## PURPOSE

This template provides a structured assessment instrument for evaluating AI system deployments against the DNAI design conditions. It is designed for use by:
- AI seaworthiness consultants conducting pre-deployment assessments
- Internal governance teams conducting periodic reviews
- Regulatory auditors evaluating compliance with high-risk AI requirements
- Research teams studying AI deployment outcomes

