### Section 4.3 — AIRD Red Flag Protocol

If any of the following are observed, deployment is placed under immediate review:
- [ ] >10% of assessed workers showing moderate-to-severe AIRD indicators
- [ ] Net workforce reduction > 0 attributable to this deployment
- [ ] Worker self-report of reduced role meaningfulness declining significantly
- [ ] Cognitive deskilling indicators in skill exercise rate monitoring

